data.description: Absolutely stunning custom built 3 bed 2.5 Ba brick home on one level. This mini farm property is a rare find with NO HOA or restrictions. You get to enjoy all the freedom of country living. Open kitchen to great room for entertaining. Extra large master bed has walk in closet, bath w/tiled shower. No Carpet! You will love the stylish & easy to maintain hardwood plank LVP flooring throughout, beautiful granites in kitchen. The large detached garage, man cave perfect for storing vehicles, tools, boat, camper. (50 amp camper hookup) Brand new deck, perfect for entertaining guests under the stars. The level fenced park like yard is perfect for quiet evenings without the noise of the big city. Easy access to I65, Hwy109, KY
